{"id":206293,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/01/广西南宁日资丰达机电公司八千员工罢工（图）/","date":"2012-01-17T10:53:59Z","modified":"2012-01-17T11:03:35Z","title":"广西南宁日资丰达机电公司八千员工罢工（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\"><a name=\"more\"></a></p>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-zdu55Tcxyag/TxUt4YgXNmI/AAAAAAAAEqs/zhwzE1r9rqg/s1600/72007-1%25E7%25BD%25A2%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E4%25B8%2580.jpg\"><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-zdu55Tcxyag/TxUt4YgXNmI/AAAAAAAAEqs/zhwzE1r9rqg/s320/72007-1%25E7%25BD%25A2%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E4%25B8%2580.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"213\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>罢工人群</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OIsfWHDvidI/TxUt9SXr75I/AAAAAAAAEq0/7mx5XkAOsLg/s1600/72007-2%25E7%25BD%25A2%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E4%25BA%258C.jpg\"><img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-OIsfWHDvidI/TxUt9SXr75I/AAAAAAAAEq0/7mx5XkAOsLg/s320/72007-2%25E7%25BD%25A2%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E4%25BA%258C.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"237\" height=\"320\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>罢工人群</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Gf9WRhtQgp8/TxUuA8p7yBI/AAAAAAAAEq8/BX49b2XEs2s/s1600/72007-3%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A3%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2591%2598%25E5%25B0%2586%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AE%25AE%25E8%2581%258C%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25B5%25B6%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%258E%2582%25E5%258C%25BA.jpg\"><img src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Gf9WRhtQgp8/TxUuA8p7yBI/AAAAAAAAEq8/BX49b2XEs2s/s320/72007-3%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E8%25A3%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2591%2598%25E5%25B0%2586%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AE%25AE%25E8%2581%258C%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25B5%25B6%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%258E%2582%25E5%258C%25BA.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"232\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>武装人员将抗议职工赶回厂区</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" align=\"center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3uQMsHqm4AI/TxUuGB_2oiI/AAAAAAAAErE/ZFGVGZ7GBY8/s1600/72007-4%25E6%25B6%258C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%258E%2582%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AE%25AE%25E8%2581%258C%25E5%25B7%25A5.jpg\"><img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3uQMsHqm4AI/TxUuGB_2oiI/AAAAAAAAErE/ZFGVGZ7GBY8/s320/72007-4%25E6%25B6%258C%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%258E%2582%25E5%25A4%2596%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AE%25AE%25E8%2581%258C%25E5%25B7%25A5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"210\" border=\"0\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>涌出厂外的抗议职工</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span><strong><br />\n</strong></span></div>\n<div><strong><span>（维权网信息员萧和协报道）</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span>日</span><span>，广西南宁日资企业丰达机电公司八千人名员工罢工抗议。起因是厂方取消年终奖，引起基层员工不满。政府出动上千警察、治安队和武警在现场戒备，并封锁工厂大门，防止工人上街游行。 </span></div>\n<div><span>事发南宁市高新技术开发区丰达机电厂区。上午<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>点，部分工人到厂长办公室示威，要求发放年终奖和延长年假，仅十多分钟，大量工人开始罢工加入示威，并有部分工人开始走出工厂门外的安吉路，准备示威游行。</span></div>\n<div><span>约半个小时后，上千名武装人员来到现场，将安吉路上的示威人员驱赶回厂区，并关闭大门。示威者在厂区内继续静坐，拒绝复工。直到下午两点，一名厂方领导才现身安抚，他希望大家先复工，对于员工的意见，他表示会向老总提出。在大量武装人员的监督下，罢工人群逐渐散去。</span></div>\n<div><span>据了解，厂方决定年三十放年假，年初七上班，期间不允许工人请假。由于春节假期太短，导致很多外省工人无法回家过年。湖北的李先生告诉本网信息员，春节只有七天假期，回家来回需要四天时间，他根本没法过一个好年。</span></div>\n<div><span>参与罢工的张女士表示，她们每天工作十多个小时，年终奖才五六百元，却要被取消，而有关系的管理阶层年终奖却高达上万元，付出和回报根本不成正比，这非常不公平。</span></div>\n<div><span>据资料显示，丰达电机（南宁）有限公司，成立于<span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span>月，是日本<span lang=\"EN-US\">FOSTER</span>（丰达）集团旗下之独资企业。日本<span lang=\"EN-US\">FOSTER</span>电机株式会社成立于<span lang=\"EN-US\">1949</span>年，是东京证券交易所一级上市公司之一。丰达电机（南宁）有限公司现有在籍员工<span lang=\"EN-US\">12000</span>人。</span></div>\n<div><span>丰达电机（南宁）有限公司电话：<span lang=\"EN-US\">0771-5688024</span></span></div>\n<div><span>参与罢工人员的电话应相关当事人请求暂不刊出，请向维权网索取。</span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-7227241345193819597?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/01/e8e93b0a425B82580.jpg-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" width=\"450\" height=\"309\"></iframe></p>\n<form action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\" method=\"POST\">定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n<input type=\"text\" name=\"EMAIL\" value=\"\" size=\"25\" maxlength=\"64\" /> <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"FEEDID\" value=\"738338\" /> <input type=\"hidden\" name=\"PUBLISHER\" value=\"7485568\" /> <input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\" /></form>\n","author":1002,"categories":[20534],"tags":[9685,16637,10778]}